               <p>NEW COURT.</p>
               <p>(1st DAY.)</p>
               <p>Middlesex Cases, Third Jury, Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>2. 
               <persName id="t18241202-2-defend121" type="defendantName">
                  MARK 
                  ALLEN
               <interp inst="t18241202-2-defend121" type="surname" value="ALLEN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241202-2-defend121" type="given" value="MARK"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241202-2-defend121" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241202-2-defend121" type="age" value="49"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18241202-2-off6" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18241202-2-off6" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241202-2-off6" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18241202-2-cd7" type="crimeDate">15th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241202-2-off6 t18241202-2-cd7"></join>, 8 lbs. of sheet copper, value 3 s., and 2 lbs. of nails, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18241202-2-victim122" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Forest
               <interp inst="t18241202-2-victim122" type="surname" value="Forest"></interp>
